Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵梅露…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经给她服用了依替唑仑  不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}依替唑仑：有强力的镇静催眠作用的药物，\N用于治疗神经症和抑郁症导致的焦虑紧张和睡眠障碍。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这份恩情我会尽早还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今后就无法再帮你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵梅露…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身体怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么  别这样看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生  满大小姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很有女仆风范
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然  因为我是大家的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满大小姐您今天也要全力傲娇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  才不是什么当然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很少见满大小姐得了感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来您的身体已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让你们担心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须表现出我满大小姐还健在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这种表现我觉得根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐  哥哥  我们出去玩踩影子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外面天气那么好  能够尽情踩个够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳菜她啊  一直吵着要和雄二玩踩影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还学人家空拳练习搞什么空脚踩影练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道她在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 想象跟影子玩踩影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被单词耍的团团转一般混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前拜托你的打扫工作  完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  已经好好完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有事的话  就快点说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就直接问了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是另一个满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的满怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎骗不过你的眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  她不会再浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她已经沉入了深深的黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我刚才说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓  这是她自己所决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请别再打扰她了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  雄二君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二君…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  小岭幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于满大小姐  我有些事想和您商量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天  满大小姐感冒的时候  交给我保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知有何用意  让我今后无论发生什么都不要把盒子还给她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要向她提起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像上了锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  所以我有点困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然交给我保管了  就必须要把里面打扫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是因为无法打开  所以我准备了电锯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滋滋滋滋  让人听着十分愉悦的马达声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能把盒子劈成两半了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在那时  我突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自将别人的东西破坏掉  这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是用电锯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是掉下来裂开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是自然的定律也没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样故意去破坏可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我的时候  如果我能确认下可以破坏到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  那么这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个盒子交给我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话你也不用烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜托您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您  那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一不小心把锁打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经开了也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打开看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  这么晚打扰你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话想和你谈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真够烦人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能别管我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我看过这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和满的交换日记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会因为心脏移植  而被之前的人格附体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是B级恐怖片的剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么荒谬  摆在眼前的事实也只能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她再也不会回到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对此很反对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个身体是属于她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她并未改变她的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么人会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界实在太悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要结束这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是你的身体  你的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白  但是我没有继续下去的自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  想把之后的自己交托于你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你的话  一定能好好生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  如果是满本人所说  那也许就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…  我觉得她接下来也应该用这副身体活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果满她不回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就可以自由地活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想人生重新再来一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许的确是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这不是我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你的意思就是想按满的想法做是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  你和这个身体变成怎么样都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是将满真正的想法作为最优先事项是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是满为了压制你而吃的药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你服下这药应该就能让满出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要向她本人确认她的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你做这种事也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经不会再…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话给我吃药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  就让你多吃点让它效果好点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想确认真正的你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧  别逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还有一丁点想活下去的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拼上这条命救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  把你真正的心意告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满  说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会照你所希望的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  快说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说清楚点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想死…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不想再失去任何东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与其让我再失去谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如让我  就这么死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那么我就照你的意思去做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我得先准备一个让世界终结的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  身体动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身体动不了是因为我给你注射了肌肉松弛剂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再过一会效用就会消散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照以前的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把你埋在你喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来你就会孤零零地呆在深深的洞里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盖上厚厚的土
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想出来也出不来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你想要的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在这箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢接受死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在同一个地方出错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师不是教过你该怎么说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个吊车尾  笨蛋  一无是处的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好想死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  喊声1 2就跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好狡猾  一死了之太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想她死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是松岛满
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  竟然在这种情况下自我介绍？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我有生以来第一次交到的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  满
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是挚友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本想这么对她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原本心脏就不好的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于失去了挚友带来的打击使得病情恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最终在美国做了心脏移植手术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  放心吧  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的软弱由我来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我们会一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  让我们成为挚友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的挚友只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要你救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能救我的  只有她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕  一片漆黑好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊  我不要呆在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵梅露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说了想让这个世界终结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么事到如今却感到害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明很想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却突然间毫无理由地结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明能好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要轻生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  因为我一直都在失去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕以后会失去更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能改变你的只有你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果做不到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一直沉沦在黑暗中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会自己漏水出去  真是个奇怪的杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那时  我选择了这个生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我本就一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以伪装起来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伪装成对周围的人有益的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让周围的人能任意将情绪发泄到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿当一个被人笑话的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不再需要做我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  满
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们永远在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是说好了要当挚友的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你变讨厌我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在依然喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我最喜欢的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那今后让我们永远在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你变讨厌我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  喜欢  现在依然是最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我最珍视的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不再是这个世界的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须向前走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一直看着过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见见大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见见雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺快的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从埋下你到现在才三天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满嘴说着想死  却这么没骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是梦  是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样  醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就不想消失  不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我打从一开始就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我等着你自己破开那个壳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多久  我都会等着你从箱子里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  如果  如果我不出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天知道  我没想过你会不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的职责就是等你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有计划B
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然作为计划来说不够全面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这三天一直在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我把你关在箱里  哪还有脸自己填饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就三天而已  没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟约会傻等差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫约会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还活着吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我真死了你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那箱子我弄了不少保险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我为了确认你的意志给你喂了药对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是汽水糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  只是汽水糖？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  因为只是汽水糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不会起任何效用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真心不想死所以才出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对雄二…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是你要活下去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家对你才没什么想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么想法你还抱那么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的错觉  都是你的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别把脸凑过来  热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你背着我我还能放哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还能带我到这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二你到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意这种小事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到我还能再次回到这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法让你变回原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我能把你带回原来的父母身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你所愿  我就帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是满所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶在晚饭前回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都来到这了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别犹豫赶紧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过我家不需要地毯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是日本人的女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用上了一般不会用的门路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以费了不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  这人情我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  人情在下次工作时加倍奉还就行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢  有成果了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  雄二君  满
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从此以后  内面的满再也没有出现…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  之前拜托你的打扫工作  完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  已经打扫完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有出现才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔跑出来  支援一下那个笨蛋傲娇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摸头摸头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她们能好好共存
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  这奇妙的故事就此告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界往前便是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,往后便是回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,取下一角便是故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:22:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是那些故事中的一部分而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40.8\pos(1020.8,751.6)}Raison d'être
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  存在理由
